@startuml CalendarScheduling
left to right direction

actor "User" as user
actor "System" as system
actor "Instructor" as instructor
actor "External Calendar" as external_calendar

rectangle "Calendar & Scheduling System" {
  usecase "View Calendar" as UC2201
  usecase "Aggregate Events" as aggregate_events
  usecase "Create Event" as UC2202
  usecase "Validate Date" as validate_date
  usecase "Add Personal Event" as UC2203
  usecase "Set Privacy" as set_privacy
  usecase "Export Calendar" as UC2204
  usecase "Format iCal" as format_ical
  usecase "Sync Calendar" as UC2205
  usecase "Set Reminders" as UC2206
  usecase "Create Course Event" as create_course_event
}

' Actor Associations
user --> UC2201 : **Association**
system --> UC2202 : **Association**
user --> UC2203 : **Association**
user --> UC2204 : **Association**
system --> UC2205 : **Association**
user --> UC2206 : **Association**
instructor --> create_course_event : **Association**
external_calendar --> UC2205 : **Association**

' Use Case Relationships
UC2201 ..> aggregate_events : **<<include>>**
UC2202 ..> validate_date : **<<include>>**
UC2203 ..> set_privacy : **<<include>>**
UC2204 ..> format_ical : **<<include>>**
UC2205 ..> UC2204 : **<<extend>>**

@enduml